      "text": " First, providing exceptional access to communications\nwould force a U-turn from the best practices now being deployed to make the\nInternet more secure. These practices include forward secrecy — where decryption keys\nare deleted immediately after use, so that stealing the encryption key used by a communications\nserver would not compromise earlier or later communications."
    },
